title: After Dark 3.2 For Windows XP
description:
I looked everywhere for this, i missed after dark from the days of windows 3.1

Here it all is packaged into one.

Please read the readmes before using, or it won\&#039;t work. 

Some of the individual screensavers don\&#039;t work properly because of having too fast a CPU etc.

Do not let it modify your autoexec.bat win.ini etc when it asks, i don\&#039;t trust an old dos program because it may corrupt something.

Enjoy!
